on’s life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAuthors, AmericanxCorrespondencex19th century. 0aAuthors, AmericanxCorrespondencex20th century. 0aAuthors, AmericanxCorrespondencey19th century. 0aAuthors, AmericanxCorrespondencey20th century. 0aAuthors, Americany19th centuryvCorrespondence. 0aAuthors, Americany20th centuryvCorrespondence. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / Letters.2bisacsh1 aGoldman-Price, Irene, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030018338240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300183382423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300183382/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles